  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A speech by HRH The Prince of Wales at the Central Remembrance Ceremony at the German parliament marking the country's National Day of Mourning for victims of war.</p>

  </div>
</div>

